    • Method Detail

      • sendPacket

        public static final void sendPacket(Cmd cmdPkt)
        Attempts to send the input CmdPkt to the CFS. If this succeeds a packet will be sent, this will put a "COMMAND SENT" message in the User Activity window. If this fails, a packet will NOT be sent, and this will put a "COMMAND NOT SENT" message in the User Activity window, and print the stack trace.
        Parameters:
        cmdPkt - The command packet to send.
